# AwkUnit

**AwkUnit** is a very simple unit testing framework for [GNU Awk](http://www.gnu.org/software/gawk/).

## Installation

GNU Awk >= 4.1 is required.

1. Get the source code of Gawk: 
    * <ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/gawk>, or
    * <http://git.savannah.gnu.org/r/gawk.git>
2. Set environment variable `$AWKSRCPATH` to the path of Gawk source, build and install:

```
$ AWKSRCPATH=/usr/src/gawk-4.1.0 make
$ make install
```

